.SS SOPS Integration
.TP
.B keys sops\-ingest \fIFILE\fR
Decrypt a SOPS-encrypted file and ingest its key-value pairs into the KeePassXC
credential store under the RemoteJuggler/SOPS/{path} group.
Requires \fBsops\fR and \fBage\fR to be installed.
.TP
.B keys sops\-sync \fIFILE\fR
Bidirectional sync of a SOPS-encrypted file with the credential store.
Detects additions, updates, and deletions. Returns counts for each operation.
.TP
.B keys sops\-export
Export the age private key from the credential store.
Derives and returns the corresponding age public key via \fBage-keygen\fR.
.RS
.TP
.B \-\-group =\fIGROUP\fR
KeePassXC group containing the age key (default: RemoteJuggler/SOPS).
.RE
